Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.00,0:00:17.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,创界山再次出现了危机
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.80,0:00:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由于连接魔界与神部界的大门被打开
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.10,0:00:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,创界山产生了巨大的崩坏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:25.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔界的魔物也陆续来袭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.10,0:00:27.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要想关闭大门的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.80,0:00:31.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有拿到天部界的"剑龙之勾玉"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.70,0:00:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 天部界是我们不能接近的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.42,0:00:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使如此 为了拯救神部界也不得不去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.10,0:00:56.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,350)}—\h没有终结之时的物语\h—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.00,0:01:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,2000)}天部界之岚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.13,0:01:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是天部界?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.43,0:01:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.64,0:01:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为是个更壮观的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.32,0:01:48.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说得这么轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.32,0:01:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 关于"剑龙之勾玉" 还是问问别人比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:55.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.10,0:01:56.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.55,0:01:59.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道"剑龙之勾玉"在哪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.00,0:02:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是不知道才要这样向前走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.25,0:02:07.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问问大龙光帝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.20,0:02:08.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是天部界的国王吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.32,0:02:11.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那大龙光帝在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.51,0:02:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来只能边走边找了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.26,0:02:22.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是神部界的人是禁止进入天部界的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.82,0:02:25.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想大龙光帝也不会见我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.02,0:02:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就碰碰运气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是魔界的魔神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.21,0:02:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你说要碰运气的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.55,0:02:54.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.34,0:02:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是为了拿到"剑龙之勾玉"而从神部界来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.09,0:03:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神部界来的!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.87,0:03:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.25,0:03:05.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们以为这里是哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.36,0:03:10.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.95,0:03:17.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里可是禁止神部界的人进入的天部界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神部界有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.10,0:03:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔界的人正要把通向神部界之门打开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎样 也不容许闯入天部界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:34.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无名小卒 看我把你们捏个粉碎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.09,0:03:37.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们才不是无名小卒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.30,0:03:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快放开海火子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.88,0:03:43.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大胆家伙 想与天部界对抗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就让你尝尝天罚的滋味吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.90,0:03:53.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.35,0:04:20.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是天部界的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.30,0:04:25.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡可是从魔界之人手中拯救神部界的救世主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.29,0:04:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.71,0:04:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.81,0:04:31.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救世主…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.70,0:04:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来神部界已沦落到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.66,0:04:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得不由这样的小孩来保护呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.97,0:04:39.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.20,0:04:41.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四天龙王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四天龙王…天部界的神子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.48,0:04:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要"剑龙之勾玉"吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:51.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在问你是不是想要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.50,0:04:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此之前 先放了海火子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想命令我吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.00,0:05:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.02,0:05:09.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修罗童子和霸翔童子是天部界的守门人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.56,0:05:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我一声令下 他就会没命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.16,0:05:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跪地求饶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:27.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们并没有做坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.00,0:05:36.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是来拜托你门协助拯救神部界的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.68,0:05:39.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何都需要"剑龙之勾玉"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.10,0:05:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你告诉我"剑龙之勾玉"在什么地…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:52.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 我就告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"剑龙之勾玉"就在由此向南越过两百座山
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.78,0:06:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两百个湖 两百座森林的玄圣山那里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.53,0:06:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玄圣山?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.90,0:06:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭你的双脚要花上多少年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:10.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么说是来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是这匹麟王 只要一飞就能到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样 要抢走麟王吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.67,0:06:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是抢也要试一试
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.54,0:06:25.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光龙剑被…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.70,0:06:43.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让我看看拯救神部界的救世主的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:47.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要不被修罗童子和霸翔童子抓到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.50,0:06:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并拿到那把剑的话 就让你骑麟王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.02,0:07:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.20,0:07:24.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好 渡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.21,0:07:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神部界的救世主就只有这点能耐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.30,0:08:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.30,0:08:07.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.90,0:08:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在见到"剑龙之勾玉"之前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救世主渡 你就会死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这前面有操纵龙的一族
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.89,0:09:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"剑龙之勾玉"就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.50,0:09:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:20.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只凭我们可能拿不到"剑龙之勾玉"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能请你也一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别得意忘形
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.10,0:09:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光是让神部界的你们活着 你们就该感恩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.95,0:09:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.10,0:09:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带我们到这里真是莫大的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.65,0:09:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么让他回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.34,0:09:48.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是天部界的神子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.72,0:09:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定能让操龙之族立刻交出"剑龙之勾玉"啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.63,0:09:55.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许是这样 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.81,0:09:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更重要的是 我们怎么回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.10,0:10:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 先去那个山谷看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.25,0:10:02.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 渡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.53,0:10:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.34,0:10:39.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像…有种不可思议的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.51,0:10:45.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎很久以前曾经来过这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.65,0:10:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.91,0:10:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说得对 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.94,0:10:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先别说了 口很渴了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.35,0:10:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.60,0:11:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.20,0:11:06.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥璐 放下刀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:20.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"剑龙之勾玉"是千年一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.48,0:11:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙之王者剑龙从天而降时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.44,0:11:27.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才会在这里出现的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千年一次!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.70,0:11:34.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时 我们龙之一族会诞生一个婴儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"剑龙之勾玉"就会变成那孩子的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.52,0:11:43.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那现在"剑龙之勾玉"就在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没有时间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底有没有 快告诉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.80,0:11:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.83,0:11:58.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"剑龙之勾玉"是千年前前往遥远世界的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.36,0:12:00.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑龙士的生命化成的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑龙士?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.26,0:12:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 新的剑龙士就快诞生了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 剑龙就会从天而降吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.93,0:12:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 那就可以拿到"剑龙之勾玉"了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.79,0:12:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.79,0:12:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"剑龙之勾玉"是龙剑士的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.50,0:12:26.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.20,0:12:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们非救神部界不可啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.25,0:12:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是剑龙…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.85,0:12:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑龙从天而降了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.79,0:13:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快迎接剑龙降临
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.73,0:13:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,点火
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是…剑龙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:31.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是开始做什么事了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.48,0:14:35.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诞生永远的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远的生命…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.60,0:14:47.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一个"无尽"要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:49.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.61,0:14:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和…和我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:04.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救世主渡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"剑龙之勾玉"可不能那么轻易让你得到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.25,0:15:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阎罗王
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.66,0:15:22.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.45,0:15:26.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.22,0:15:32.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快躲开…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.78,0:15:40.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去保护剑龙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.22,0:15:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Adaru
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.65,0:16:00.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.70,0:16:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是它的对手 快躲开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.30,0:16:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借来一用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.08,0:16:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道这里是哪里吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.40,0:16:19.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是救世主的出生地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.55,0:16:22.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.48,0:16:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时也是你的葬身之地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.26,0:16:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.58,0:17:14.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑龙…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.45,0:17:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑龙…在哭?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.58,0:18:23.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑龙的…婴儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.52,0:18:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是"剑龙之勾玉"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.70,0:18:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想得到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.10,0:18:49.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.00,0:18:59.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑被…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.84,0:19:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.20,0:19:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.86,0:19:28.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一来神部界就属于我们魔界的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吼鬼 把剑龙和救世主一起埋葬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.13,0:19:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.70,0:19:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Adaru…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.75,0:20:22.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四天龙王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天部界的神子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:29.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我原以为还没到和你决胜负的时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.55,0:20:31.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪恶之徒 退下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:38.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毁灭神部界之后就轮到天部界了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.35,0:20:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时再一决胜负吧 四天龙王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.29,0:20:50.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会记着的 阎罗王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.20,0:21:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎样都已经得不到"剑龙之勾玉"了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.15,0:21:09.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 渡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"剑龙之勾玉"是为了成就救世主的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.70,0:21:19.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千年诞生一次的剑龙士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.87,0:21:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是为了完成下一任救世主的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:28.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的剑龙士 换言之救世主 就是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:33.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"剑龙之勾玉"正由你持有着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:40.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所拥有的"剑龙之勾玉"就能拯救神部界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:43.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并没拥有那样东西 在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.26,0:21:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在你的体内
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.27,0:21:47.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的体内?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是获得"剑龙之勾玉"的剑龙士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.70,0:21:56.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑龙的孩子!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.38,0:22:27.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虎王!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.52,0:22:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么虎王会…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.19,0:22:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡 海火子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.50,0:22:38.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 本少爷在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.37,0:22:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虎王
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.78,0:22:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡 好想见你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.31,0:22:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是剑龙将虎王带回原来的世界了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.89,0:22:51.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.49,0:22:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是白龙马吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.43,0:22:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白龙马?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.05,0:22:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白龙的化身
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.73,0:23:00.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了回报拚命守护龙的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.19,0:23:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白龙就变成这般模样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.20,0:23:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听从那个人的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.82,0:23:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白龙它…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.79,0:23:10.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为保护天部界的奖赏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.48,0:23:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把这匹麟王借给你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.27,0:23:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有这两匹马在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.53,0:23:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你们的战斗也会有些帮助吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.96,0:23:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.46,0:23:27.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我们就回神部界去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.33,0:23:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别输给魔界的那些家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.60,0:23:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会输呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.90,0:23:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥璐也要保重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.10,0:23:36.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干 干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.90,0:23:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.77,0:23:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.84,0:23:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Adaru…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.66,0:23:48.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远的生命 没有终结之时
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.82,0:23:53.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新诞生的剑龙士已不再是救世主了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.40,0:23:58.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然没有获得"剑龙之勾玉"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.10,0:24:01.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 却得到了其代替品
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.04,0:24:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是救世主渡 你的心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.19,0:24:14.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虎王 回到神部界后
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.81,0:24:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就要面临和魔界之人的战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.00,0:24:18.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.66,0:24:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 快点走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.43,0:25:13.41,jpoped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}耳をふさいでも 聞こえていたの
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.37,0:25:20.58,jpoped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}時の砂が落ちる音
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.71,0:25:28.92,jpoped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}黃昏に金の雲を残して
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.51,0:25:35.72,jpoped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}沈む夕陽をせつなく見る
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.93,0:25:47.65,jpoped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Adieu 悲しみの 夜は來るけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.94,0:25:51.70,jpoped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}淚 見せない
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.99,0:25:55.45,jpoped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}永遠の扉を
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.73,0:26:06.92,jpoped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}開けば始まる 終わりなき時の物語
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.21,0:26:10.88,jpoped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}出逢いは一瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.09,0:26:14.68,jpoped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}でも胸に Memory
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.14,0:26:26.44,jpoped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,350)}君の熱さを忘れないよ Forever
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.43,0:25:13.41,cnoped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}即使堵上耳朵也能听见
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.37,0:25:20.58,cnoped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}沙漏漏下的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.71,0:25:28.92,cnoped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}黄昏时只残留金色的云
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.51,0:25:35.72,cnoped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}难过的看着夕阳落下
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.93,0:25:47.65,cnoped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Adieu 悲伤的夜晚到来
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.94,0:25:51.70,cnoped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}却不让你看见泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.99,0:25:55.45,cnoped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}只要开启永远的门扉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.73,0:26:06.92,cnoped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}永恒的传说就会开始
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.21,0:26:10.88,cnoped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}虽然只有瞬间的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.09,0:26:14.68,cnoped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}但胸中的 Memory
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.14,0:26:26.44,cnoped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,350)}不会忘记你的热情 Forever
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.19,0:26:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神部界失去了神部七龙神的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.37,0:26:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对魔界的攻击只能坐以待毙
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.95,0:27:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们都受了伤 不得不退出战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.76,0:27:08.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和虎王 海火子一起来到通向魔界的大门那里
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.68,0:27:11.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 "剑龙之勾玉"并不在我手中
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.95,0:27:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信念 信念就是我最后的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.85,0:27:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远的传说

